{{ja-kanjitab|ともし|yomi=k}}

First attested around the 10th century.

From {{m|ja|点し|tr=tomoshi}}, the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of verb {{m|ja|点す|tr=tomosu||to [[light]]}}.

{{ja-noun|kyu=燈|ともし}}

# a [[light]]
# {{altspell|lang=ja|照射|tr=tomoshi|nodot=1|sort=ともし}}: a [[torch]] used to [[bait]] [[deer]] when [[night]] [[hunting]]

{{ja-kanjitab|ともしび|yomi=k}}

Compound of {{com|ja|sort=ともしひ|点し|tr1=tomoshi|pos1=the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of verb {{m|ja|点す|tr=tomosu}}, “to [[light]]”‎|火|tr2=hi|t2=[[fire]]}}.

{{rendaku2|sort=ともしひ|hi|bi}}

{{ja-noun|kyu=燈|ともしび}}

# a [[light]]
#* {{quote-song|year=1986|lyricist={{w|Hayao Miyazaki}}|composer={{w|Joe Hisaishi}}|title={{w2|ja|君をのせて (井上あずみの曲)|君をのせて}}|trans-title=Reaching You|album=|url=|artist={{w|Azumi Inoue}}|lang=ja}}
#*: {{ja-usex|sort=ともしひ|地球はまわる君をかくして　輝く瞳きらめく'''灯'''...|^ちきゅう は まわる きみ を かくして　かがやく ひとみ きらめく '''ともしび'''...|The Earth spins, hiding your shining pupils and glittering '''lights'''.}}
#: {{syn|ja|明かり|tr=akari|灯火|tr2=tōka}}
# a [[lit]] [[flame]] {{gl|such as of a [[candle]] or [[torch]]}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=ともしび|historical|obsolete}} under the {{w|Ritsuryō}} system in the {{w|Heian period}}, a kind of [[scholarship]] granted to [[university]] [[student]]s

{{ja-kanjitab|とぼし|yomi=k}}

From {{m|ja|点し|tr=toboshi}}, the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of verb {{m|ja|点す|tr=tobosu||to [[light]]|pos=archaic}}.

Equivalent to a shift from ''tomoshi'' above, the nasal {{IPAchar|/-m-/}} becomes plosive {{IPAchar|/-b-/}}.

{{ja-noun|kyu=燈|とぼし}}

# {{lb|ja|archaic|sort=とほし}} an [[indoor]] [[torch]]
# {{lb|ja|archaic}} ''Same as {{m|ja||ともし|tr=tomoshi}} above''

{{ja-kanjitab|とぼしび|yomi=irr}}

Compound of {{com|ja|点し|tr1=toboshi|pos1=the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of verb {{m|ja|点す|tr=tobosu}}, “to [[light]]”‎, archaic|火|tr2=hi|t2=[[fire]]}}. {{rendaku2|hi|bi}}

Equivalent to a shift from ''tomoshibi'' above, the nasal {{IPAchar|/-m-/}} becomes plosive {{IPAchar|/-b-/}}.

{{ja-noun|kyu=燈|あかし}}

# a [[light]], [[lamp]]
#* {{quote-song|year=1987|lyricist={{w|lang=ja|たかたかし|Takashi Taka}}|composer={{w|lang=ja|猪俣公章|Kōshō Inomata}}|title={{w2|ja|あばれ太鼓}}|trans-title=Raging Drums|album=|url=|artist={{w|Fuyumi Sakamoto}}|lang=ja}}
#*: {{ja-usex|[[櫓%太%鼓]]の'''灯'''がゆれて　揃い[[浴衣]]の夏がゆく|やぐら%-だい%こ の '''あかし''' が ゆれて　そろい ゆかた の なつ が ゆく|The festival-commencing '''lamp''' sways, all in summer ''[[yukata]]'' have come.}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=あかし|Shinto|Buddhism}} a light {{gl|or [[lighted]] [[lamp]]}} offered to a ''[[kami]]'' or [[buddha]]
#: {{syn|ja|[[御灯]], [[御明かし]], [[御灯明]]|tr=miakashi}}

